      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests and method-of-manufactured-solutions verification must be demonstrated for the hemolysis transport equations.",
      "rationale": "Only standard benchmark cases (lid-driven cavity, pipe flow) were used for code verification. Hemolysis transport equation verification via manufactured solutions was not performed. Achieved level 2 is below required level 4."
