      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (e.g., E_rel) must be computed with uncertainty bounds for all primary QOIs across all validation experiments.",
      "rationale": "Relative error in normalized index of hemolysis was computed for 4 of 5 operating points with partial uncertainty quantification. One operating point lacked experimental replication. Achieved level 3 is below required level 4."
    },
    {
