      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation QOIs must be identical to COU QOIs (absolute hemolysis index) or a demonstrated surrogate with quantified mapping uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Validation used normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) while COU requires absolute plasma free hemoglobin concentration. Mapping between NIH and absolute hemolysis introduces unquantified uncertainty. Achieved level 3 is below required level 5."
    },
    {
