      "acceptanceCriteria": "The hemolysis damage accumulation model form must be justified against competing constitutive models with sensitivity analysis demonstrating dominance of selected form.",
      "rationale": "Power-law hemolysis model was selected without comparison to Giersiepen-Wurzinger or modified stress-based models. Model form uncertainty is a dominant source of prediction error at MRL 5 and was not formally assessed. Achieved level 2 is below required level 5."
