    "rationale": "Despite all 13 credibility factors showing achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5, and 6 factors flagged as epistemic gaps, the credibility assessment package is accepted as a complete documentation artifact for regulatory submission. The decision reflects acceptance of the package structure and evidence compilation, not acceptance of the model for clinical use. Note: this package carries a declared ed25519 signature algorithm and a valid sha256 content hash, but the signature value itself is absent — structural integrity of this UnitOfAssurance cannot be independently verified.",
